headline: Wall Street Bulls Look Optimistic About Delta (DAL): Should You Buy?
summary: Based on the average brokerage recommendation (ABR), Delta (DAL) should be added to one's portfolio. Wall Street analysts' overly optimistic recommendations cast doubt on the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric. So, is the stock worth buying?
